			  			I think Blockade is abused too often. They abuse it beacuse they don't care about Honor. Which is why I suggest that honor should have more effects on everything. I don't know if this ever happened to you but...here's a situation<br />
<br />
-You attack someone at your OWN power and you win.(You won the battle fair and square)<br />
-The ennemy is online and because really outrageous and calls upon an ally to attack you.Yes  It's allowed to call help from the others. But he calls an ally who is really more powerful than you, 100% more powerful than you.<br />
-His ally blockades you since its 50% down for blockade<br />
-Your fleets gets raped.<br />
-The ennemy sents 1 fleet by 1 to steals planet.(no Fleet Battle)<br />
<br />
It is unfair, abusing blockade and cheap. And also boring because you have no choice but to die.<br />
<br />
So im just suggesting something to prevent these things to make this game more fun and more FAIR.<br />
(yes stealing planets is fun but I find killing fleets are more fun! Don't you think so? )						<P align=right> </P>
