			  	the simple answer is to have honor give several bonuses to fleets and economy.<br />
<br />
bonuses to fleets: higher honor gives + % to fleet dammage, ship hit points, commander exp gained vs. equal opponets. faster repair rate.<br />
<br />
bonuses to economy: higher honor means you are more respected in trade. gives a +CM to commerce or an added % to current commerce. high honor makes your people more patriotic giveing you a +CM to military<br />
<br />
well it might not prevent the nasty blockaids but it would help.			   <P align=right></P>
